com.qozix.tileview.tiles

Interface TileCanvasView.TileCanvasDrawListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TileCanvasViewGroup
    Enclosing class:
    TileCanvasView

    public static interface TileCanvasView.TileCanvasDrawListener
    Interface definition for callbacks to be invoked when drawing is complete. A "pending" draw is one that indicates tile transitions states are still pending and and immediate redraw should be requested. A "complete" draw callback will only be invoked if transitions are enabled, and will occur the first time a "complete" draw is complete after a "pending" draw.
